(83, 'columns/May2023/LgUmMAsjFZCdQCj30gLd.jpg', 'Rossiya Federatsiyasining Chelyabinsk shahridagi \"Durem\", \"Uzbechka\", \"Sultan\" milliy restoranlar tarmog‘i haqida bilasizmi?', 'Россия Федерациясининг Челябинск шаҳридаги \"Дурем\", \"Узбечка\", \"Sultan\" миллий ресторанлар тармоғи ҳақида биласизми?', 'Знаете ли вы о национальной сети ресторанов \"Дарем\", \"узбечка\", \"Султан\" в Челябинске, РФ?', 'Do you know about the National Restaurant chain \"Durham\", \"Uzbechka\", \"Sultan\" in Chelyabinsk, Russian Federation?', '<p>Rossiya Federatsiyasining Chelyabinsk shahridagi \"Durem\", \"Uzbechka\", \"Sultan\" milliy restoranlar tarmog&lsquo;i haqida bilasizmi?<br>Loyihamizning navbatdagi sonida vatandoshimiz Dostonbek Isroilov asos solgan mazkur milliy taomlar maskani haqida ma&rsquo;lumot oling!</p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fjfkAzNSOXI\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>Agar siz Chelyabinsk shahriga tashrif buyursangiz havolalar orqali milliy oshxonalar manzilini topishingiz mumkin:</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/%D0%A8%D0%90%D0%A3%D0%A0%D0%9C%D0%90+DUREM/@55.1885153,61.3334486,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x43c5933c9772bd49:0xba882def577b550e!8m2!3d55.1885153!4d61.3334486\">📍 Birinchi manzil</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/%D1%83%D0%BB.+%D0%92%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%B1%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%8F,+%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BA,+%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%8F+%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%BB.,+%D0%A0%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%81%D0%B8%D1%8F,+454080/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x43c592bddffbefe9:0x5c901545ef29b83d!7e2!8m2!3d55.153476999999995!4d61.367666199999995?utm_source=mstt_1&amp;entry=gps\">📍Ikkinchi manzil</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/%D1%83%D0%BB.+%D0%92%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%B1%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%8F,+%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BA,+%D0%A7%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F%D0%B1%D0%B8%D0%BD